px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　2. 负责公司的生产经营全面管理工作，制定公司投资发展策略及经营计划，大力开拓特车市场业务，不断提升市场份额;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　3.负责公司生产管理、成本管理、质量、安全、环境和职业健康管理等工作;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　4.负责日常投资管理工作，同时建立并维系与合作机构等多方的业务关系;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　5.董事会授予的其他职权和工作。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">三、组织机构</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　为确保整个招聘过程的顺利进行，成立由淮海工业集团领导及相关部门负责人组成的招聘工作领导组及招聘工作办公室。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">四、工作程序</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　公开招聘按照发布公告、组织报名、资格审查、实施竞聘、组织考察、会议讨论、公示、办理聘任手续等程序进行，对聘用人员实行试用期制，试用期为一年。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">(一)个人报名</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　符合报名资格条件的人员自愿报名参与招聘。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">(二)资格审查</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　招聘工作组根据预设条件，对报名应聘人员进行资格审查。监督组负责资格审查过程的监督工作。对通过资格审查的人员，我们将以电话方式通知。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　如少于等于1人报名或报名人选经资格审查符合任职资格条件少于等于1人的，该职位不再组织公开招聘，采用组织选拔的方式聘用。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">(三)应聘成绩</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　应聘人员竞聘成绩包括笔试、面试和业绩评价组成，在前三名人选中择优录用。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　通过资格审查应聘人员参加笔试，笔试成绩合格者(原则上分数在及格线以上)取前5名(有并列者，同时进入;不足5名的，笔试分数及格者进入)进入面试。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　面试包括竞职演讲、现场答辩。每位应聘人员按照抽签顺序号，依次参加面试。应聘人员根据竞聘岗位主要职责，从岗位认知、工作中的亮点业绩及不足、履职思路等方面进行演讲，时间不超过15分钟;现场答辩由面试评委(评委由淮海工业集团相关领导及外部评委组成)现场提问，应聘人员结合工作实际进行回答，时间不超过20分钟。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　应聘人员须于参加面试之日起提前二个工作日提交竞聘报告，主要内容包括个人工作经历、突出业绩、对应聘职位的认识，下一步工作思路及近三年目标措施等。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">(四)考察及任职</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　考察人选在本岗位应聘人员总成绩前三名中确定。确定人选后，党委工作部按照《淮海工业集团中级经营管理者管理办法》对被考察人员履行考察(背景调查)及任职程序。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">五、工作待遇</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　与淮海集团签订用工合同，试用期一年，基准年薪为人民币20万元/年，根据年度目标责任书各项指标约定的激励条款考核发放(以2018年度主要指标考核完成情况为基准，同时满足以下条件：利润每增长100万元、劳产率每增长10%、存货和应收占收入比重每下降10%奖励5万元，上不封顶)。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">六、招聘说明</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　1.报名截止时间：2018年12月18日</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; margin-top: 20px !important; line-height: 23px !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important; font-family: SimSun !important;\">　　2.报名方式：通过淮海工业集团门户网下载报名表，填写完毕后发送至电子信箱：<a href=\"mailto:allensxhh@163.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); 